page.title: 19 BIRD SURVEY (1976-84)
page.content: Bird Survey for O.S.Square 8546 {Resident Birds:}Carrion crow,Magpie, Jay,Great Tit,Blue Tit,Coal Tit,Wren, Song Thrush,Blackbird,Robin,Dunnock, Starling,Bullfinch,Chaffinch,Mallard, Canada Goose,Sparrowhawk,Kestrel, Pheasant,Moorhen,Stock Dove,Collared Dove,Tawny OWl,Kingfisher,Green and Gt.Spotted Woodpecker,Grey Heron, Jackdaw,Long-tailed Tit,Nuthatch,Tree Creeper,Mistle Thrush,Goldcrest,Pied Wagtail,Grey Wagtail,Greenfinch,Gold- finch,Woodpigeon,House Sparrow. {Summer Resident:}Blackcap,Whitetroat, Willow Warbler,Chiffchaff, Cuckoo, Swallow,Sedge Warbler,garden Warbler, Lesser Whitethroat,Spotted Flycatcher. {Occasional Res.} Coot,Skylark,Mandarin Duck,Yellowhammer,Mute Swan,Redpoll, Turtle Dove,Barn Owl,Marsh Tit,Field- fare,Nightingale,Reed Bunting,Redwing, Treesparrow,Lesserspotted Woodpecker.
